Description: # Requirements
        Python 3.8+
        
        # Local development
        
        ### Set up the project
        ```sh
        cd ~/YOUR_PATH/python-worker-public
        python3 -m venv venv
        source venv/bin/activate
        pip install -r requirements.txt
        ```
        
        ### Run tests
        ```sh
        venv/bin/python3 -m pytest tests
        ```
        
        ### Run code linter
        ```sh
        venv/bin/python3 -m flake8
        ```
        
        
        
